Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.95,0:00:13.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,掌上的微風
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.78,0:00:21.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在光芒中一閃一閃地舞動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.49,0:00:27.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已經能用全新的笑容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.43,0:00:35.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,向陌生人道早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:35.17,0:00:41.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,儘管回憶溢滿心頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.91,0:00:47.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的朝氣絕不認輸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.72,0:00:52.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無所謂在乾掉的淚痕中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.16,0:00:57.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有一扇通往夢想的門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.20,0:01:01.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果煩惱就無法前進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.33,0:01:02.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:02.73,0:01:10.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會以迎接朋友的方式\N溫柔地微笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.17,0:01:14.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是我們的約定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.85,0:01:19.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無意間悲傷雖然湧上心頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.28,0:01:23.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也會試著與人和好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:23.79,0:01:28.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為這是我們的約定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.10,0:01:40.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,音無響子從今天開始\N辭去一刻館的管理員工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.02,0:01:52.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,辭…職?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.29,0:01:59.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,#23 響子千鈞一!\N母親可怕的陰謀!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.33,0:02:05.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是我的一點心意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.20,0:02:09.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請各位嚐嚐看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.44,0:02:11.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,告辭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.75,0:02:20.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底是怎麼回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.02,0:02:22.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一之瀨太太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.12,0:02:24.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管理員有跟妳說\N她要辭職嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.95,0:02:26.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她沒跟我說啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.63,0:02:33.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起\N打擾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.49,0:02:34.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們是搬家公司的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.03,0:02:36.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請問管理室在哪裡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.97,0:02:39.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,轉角過去的那個房間就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.80,0:02:41.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打擾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.20,0:02:44.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裡拜託你了\N好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.44,0:02:49.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下,你們在幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.08,0:02:50.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然是在搬家囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.61,0:02:56.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然是在搬家?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.49,0:03:07.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來她真的辭職了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.90,0:03:13.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過,她也太不夠意思了\N至少也跟我講一聲嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.20,0:03:18.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一直把管理員\N當作自己的親妹妹看待耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.27,0:03:21.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我看是親孫女吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.34,0:03:23.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是親妹妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.48,0:03:26.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是孫女啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.66,0:03:43.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝,打擾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.49,0:04:13.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難怪我總覺得有什麼問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.73,0:04:16.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,突然間開始大肆整修起公寓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.93,0:04:20.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,俗話說“飛鳥不濁水”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.30,0:04:24.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過她真的太不夠意思了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.51,0:04:29.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裡是一刻館吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.41,0:04:35.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代,請加油喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.42,0:04:39.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是我丈夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.76,0:04:44.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好可怕喔,王子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.93,0:04:52.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我倒是想起來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.80,0:04:56.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以前那個管理員老爹\N也是突然辭職走人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.80,0:05:00.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,響子跟以前的管理員不一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.84,0:05:04.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一直把她當作一家人看待\N怎麼會…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.95,0:05:07.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼會變成這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.38,0:05:10.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真沒意思,我要去喝酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.93,0:05:22.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也一起來,一起來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.17,0:05:34.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟糕糟糕,弄到這麼晚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.58,0:05:38.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,惣一郎,對不起喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.01,0:05:41.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我馬上弄飯給你吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.85,0:05:43.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.42,0:05:47.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哎呀,真是的,門居然沒關
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.03,0:05:52.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,四谷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.23,0:05:57.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為事出突然\N我來整理一下自己的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.07,0:06:07.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這…這究竟是怎麼回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.84,0:06:11.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過,我終於理出頭緒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.18,0:06:14.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們沒有權利阻攔妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.78,0:06:17.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在說什麼啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.08,0:06:20.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛才妳母親來過這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.59,0:06:24.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說妳要辭職
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.46,0:06:27.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接著搬家公司就來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.86,0:06:30.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.17,0:06:33.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.17,0:06:34.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要回娘家問個清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.94,0:06:43.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個,送給大家吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.08,0:07:23.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我真是看錯管理員了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.65,0:07:27.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,響子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.49,0:07:34.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,晚安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.73,0:07:38.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家都喝得差不多醉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.57,0:07:40.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.67,0:07:44.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.57,0:07:48.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管理員回娘家去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.31,0:07:50.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你見到管理員了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.28,0:07:53.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對,這是餞別的禮物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.69,0:08:06.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,章魚燒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.33,0:08:11.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就這麼一盒章魚燒\N就想了斷我們的關係嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.14,0:08:20.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,響…響子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.51,0:08:22.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太過份了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.51,0:08:28.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也要吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.22,0:08:32.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,四谷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.02,0:08:35.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,帶大家回公寓去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.99,0:08:36.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.72,0:08:39.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣我根本沒辦法做生意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.29,0:08:42.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,朱美,今天妳就先回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.83,0:08:44.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣啊,不好意思喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.03,0:08:48.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走,回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.00,0:08:52.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在說什麼啊,我還沒喝夠呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.34,0:09:02.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,響子!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.61,0:09:26.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,媽媽,不要喝太多啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.64,0:09:29.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吵死了,小孩子去睡覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.98,0:09:32.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也太娘娘腔了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.45,0:09:34.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要哭到什麼時候啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.18,0:09:37.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是可是,怎麼可以這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.69,0:09:46.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這也難怪他哭得這麼傷心\N管理員太無情了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.74,0:09:59.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是誰啊?都這麼晚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.81,0:10:02.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可能是風吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.98,0:10:08.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是受不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.42,0:10:12.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.09,0:10:14.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們怎麼都在這裡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.59,0:10:17.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳才是呢\N妳回來拿忘記的東西嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.66,0:10:20.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳不是回娘家去了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.86,0:10:24.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對啊,我是去叫他們\N把我的行李送回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.16,0:10:26.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很抱歉,給大家添麻煩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.83,0:10:30.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想不到我不在的時候\N竟然會發生這種事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.54,0:10:33.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這次的事都是我媽的陰謀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.44,0:10:36.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我聽不懂妳在講什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.71,0:10:40.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總而言之,妳不會辭職吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.35,0:10:42.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然不會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.79,0:10:47.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.96,0:10:49.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代,不要這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.49,0:10:52.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什麼關係\N這是酒後真情流露啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.66,0:10:55.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了,太好了,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.43,0:10:58.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.97,0:11:05.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總之太好了,重新開始喝吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.34,0:11:07.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝,我都快渴死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.91,0:11:09.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.34,0:11:11.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為我罵得太大聲了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.09,0:11:22.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼,大家辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.86,0:11:26.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一開始就覺得有什麼問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.80,0:11:38.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.32,0:11:59.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝大家這麼關心我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.31,0:12:13.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管理員…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.50,0:12:44.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在哭什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.07,0:12:47.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有啦,因為實在太可愛了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.78,0:12:50.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你又把相簿拿出來看了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.74,0:12:53.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳自己來看看啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.68,0:12:55.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.83,0:13:09.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的好可愛啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.56,0:13:13.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以前明明是個\N純真坦誠的好孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.14,0:13:16.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,照片啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.51,0:13:23.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個可以拿來用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.95,0:13:32.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳不覺得很奇怪嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.85,0:13:34.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太奇怪了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.46,0:13:36.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我爸媽真的太反常了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.79,0:13:45.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳幹嘛這樣說妳爸媽呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.23,0:13:49.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們趁我不在的時候\N偷偷地把我的行李運走耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.17,0:13:50.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是有點過份啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.90,0:13:53.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,實在太奇怪了吧\N這根本是犯罪嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.68,0:13:59.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道你們的關係不太好嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.05,0:14:02.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看就知道了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.22,0:14:03.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼會這樣呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.32,0:14:13.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳對外人那麼溫柔善良\N怎麼會對爸媽那麼兇呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.66,0:14:16.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為對他們太好的話\N他們會得寸進尺的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.13,0:14:17.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是因為妳太嚴格了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.97,0:14:20.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,使得他們不知道如何\N表達對妳的關心吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.90,0:14:23.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳好像在幫我爸媽說話喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.04,0:14:26.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為我也是為人父母啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.84,0:14:30.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有爸媽在是很幸福的事\N我說真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.91,0:14:31.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,倒是,我問妳喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.98,0:14:34.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,賢太郎有沒有在我背後\N說我的壞話?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.95,0:14:35.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.52,0:14:42.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真討厭\N放春假也不帶人家出去玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.79,0:14:45.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,暑假的時候\N你也發過同樣的牢騷喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.00,0:14:54.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我媽一年到頭都在喝酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.80,0:14:57.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,偶爾發發牢騷\N也不會遭天譴吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.24,0:14:59.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是人小鬼大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.67,0:15:01.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在不是煩這個的時候吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.91,0:15:04.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管理員說不定會被帶走耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.95,0:15:07.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過你媽媽是個很能幹的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.98,0:15:12.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真要是出事了\N只有她能保護得了管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.59,0:15:21.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自己心愛的女人\N就要自己去保護
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.03,0:15:23.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也太沒出息了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.00,0:15:29.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過,我的確什麼都不能做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.37,0:15:34.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這種房客和管理員的關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.37,0:15:36.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管說什麼都沒有說服力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.98,0:15:40.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,畢竟我還是外人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.39,0:15:47.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,媽媽,妳怎麼啦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.92,0:15:49.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼怎麼啦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.59,0:15:52.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,實在太稀奇了\N居然會帶我去看電影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.26,0:15:54.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,偶爾也要培養一下親子感情嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.06,0:15:56.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,高不高興?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.00,0:15:57.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.00,0:16:03.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好管閒事,好奇心旺盛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.34,0:16:06.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,容易被煽動,喜歡被人依靠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.71,0:16:10.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果能拉攏到一之瀨夫人就好辦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.82,0:16:17.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是要怎麼找她出來呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.42,0:16:20.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去一刻館的話,會被響子逮到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.92,0:16:25.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,實在太巧了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.00,0:16:30.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這真是老天爺的安排啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.46,0:16:32.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.13,0:16:34.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是音無響子的母親
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.30,0:16:38.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我今天是專程來找妳聊一聊的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.24,0:16:41.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼要找我聊呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.34,0:16:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是因為…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.18,0:16:45.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,實在是太難為情了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.95,0:16:48.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在我只能靠妳了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.58,0:16:51.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,站在路邊聊也不太好…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.85,0:16:52.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,媽媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.05,0:16:56.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,意思是妳願意陪我談談嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.32,0:16:57.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.69,0:16:59.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的太感謝妳了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.33,0:17:02.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,媽媽,電影怎麼辦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.33,0:17:04.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個比電影有趣多了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.07,0:17:08.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別生氣\N我會給你吃好吃東西補償你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.40,0:17:10.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這種事再持續下去的話\N我要去學壞喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.51,0:17:15.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大嬸帶賢太郎去看電影?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.28,0:17:17.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天吹的是什麼風啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.21,0:17:21.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定是看了管理員的親子關係\N覺得很不安吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.28,0:17:23.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這種話不能亂說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.98,0:17:26.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒關係吧,這是事實嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.90,0:17:39.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了?快接啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.70,0:17:41.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我怕是我媽打來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.57,0:17:43.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真拿妳沒輒,我來幫妳接吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.47,0:17:46.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果是我媽打來的\N就說我不在家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.31,0:17:47.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.48,0:17:51.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂,這裡是一刻館
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.38,0:17:52.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有,她在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.75,0:17:55.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是男的打來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.45,0:17:59.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.82,0:18:01.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦,爸爸?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.96,0:18:05.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳媽有沒有去找妳?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.39,0:18:07.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有,怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.59,0:18:09.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是這樣的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.86,0:18:13.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想跟妳單獨談一談
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.37,0:18:16.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳媽在的話\N情況會變得很混亂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.07,0:18:18.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我現在可以過去嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.44,0:18:20.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以是可以…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.31,0:18:22.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.61,0:18:26.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.05,0:18:30.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我爸要來這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.12,0:18:36.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,臭老頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.46,0:18:39.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果他敢用蠻力\N把管理員押回去的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.59,0:18:41.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一定要揍扁他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.29,0:18:44.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要有所表現才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.64,0:18:53.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管…管理員,妳爸爸來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.61,0:18:57.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸,你來得好快喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.38,0:19:01.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是在斜坡的公共電話打給妳的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.92,0:19:03.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們迴避一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.52,0:19:11.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為雙方一直在賭氣\N現在她根本不聽爸媽的話了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.19,0:19:16.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說起來很抱歉\N我向鄰居打聽過妳的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.10,0:19:20.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳調查過我的事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.40,0:19:23.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽說妳很照顧響子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.77,0:19:27.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為響子那個人很有意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.91,0:19:30.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳說的話她一定會聽的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.95,0:19:34.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請妳幫我叫響子回家來!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.16,0:19:52.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我老公體弱多病\N經常動不動就住院
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.10,0:19:56.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真可憐啊,我還是第一次聽到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.77,0:19:59.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,響子居然都沒有來探病
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.07,0:20:02.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代哥哥說前幾天\N他有看到管理員的爸爸喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.91,0:20:05.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他一定是從醫院裡溜出來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.95,0:20:08.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他太想念響子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.85,0:20:10.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一定要儘快把響子帶回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.92,0:20:12.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不擇手段也要把她帶回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.82,0:20:14.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.72,0:20:18.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難怪妳會找搬家公司來\N用這麼強硬的方式對待她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.23,0:20:19.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來是這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.80,0:20:24.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.63,0:20:26.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會說服響子的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.77,0:20:28.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夫人,謝謝妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.00,0:20:37.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸向妳道歉\N真的很對不起妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.61,0:20:41.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以妳也別再賭氣了\N快點回家來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.98,0:20:47.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸,你強烈反對我結婚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.29,0:20:51.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有惣一郎過世時\N你也沒有來安慰我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.19,0:20:55.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,惣一郎的忌日\N你也沒去墳上給他上香
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.10,0:20:56.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然還有很多事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.40,0:20:58.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是這些事情我都不在意了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.57,0:21:03.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,響子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.74,0:21:06.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已經不是小孩子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.21,0:21:08.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自己的事,我自己會做決定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.61,0:21:14.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好不容易向她道歉了\N居然這樣…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.28,0:21:16.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要回去了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.48,0:21:17.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上廁所
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.79,0:21:28.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他還是沒聽進去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.40,0:21:32.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我進來囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.13,0:21:36.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳還是回娘家去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.87,0:21:40.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要等到\N子欲養而親不在的時候,才…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.11,0:21:41.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳怎麼突然跟我說這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.41,0:21:43.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這還需要問嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.84,0:21:47.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳也要為妳爸爸著想啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.31,0:21:50.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管怎麼樣,父母畢竟是父母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.22,0:21:52.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,更何況妳爸爸已經…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.39,0:21:54.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,繼續說,請繼續教訓她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.85,0:21:56.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是誰?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.19,0:22:01.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好意思,初次見面\N我是響子的父親
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.96,0:22:03.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.03,0:22:05.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.27,0:22:07.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看起來氣色不錯嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.50,0:22:09.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,託您的福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.10,0:22:10.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這就怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.44,0:22:13.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟照片裡完全不一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.71,0:22:14.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,照片?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:15.34,0:22:16.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,照片?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.78,0:22:21.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳媽拿了一張他長得這麼瘦\N而且還是住院時的照片給我看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:21.62,0:22:24.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是超過五年以前的照片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.38,0:22:25.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳被她騙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.99,0:22:29.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這下妳懂了吧\N我媽是個不正常的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.22,0:22:30.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我明明跟妳說過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:31.39,0:22:33.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.47,0:22:46.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你為什麼要背著我\N偷偷去找響子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.51,0:22:48.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個八婆差點就上鉤了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:48.68,0:22:50.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳是白痴啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:50.08,0:22:54.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這種漏洞百出的計劃\N肯定兩三下就穿幫了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:07.93,0:23:10.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過真的太好了\N來,喝啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:10.36,0:23:13.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過感覺還蠻冷的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:13.37,0:23:16.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是在慶祝改建完工嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:26.31,0:23:27.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.25,0:23:30.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然是這種破爛公寓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:30.55,0:23:31.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,儘管如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:31.89,0:23:34.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,儘管如此,這還是我的家啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.40,0:23:53.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今年又到了櫻花的季節
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.67,0:23:57.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,惣一郎\N在我尚未找到自己的方向之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.94,0:24:00.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要繼續冠著你的姓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.21,0:24:00.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相聚一刻下一回
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.01,0:24:03.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,「五代興奮不已!\N和小津江的初吻?」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:03.88,0:24:07.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,天啊,五代你到底在想什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:27.24,0:24:35.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那天在陌生的城市下了一場陣雨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:35.22,0:24:42.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳非常在意淋溼的高跟鞋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:42.16,0:24:50.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從前妳用那隱藏著\N稚氣的側臉和我交談
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:50.13,0:24:56.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳說的話語至今仍能想起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:56.37,0:25:03.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一開始就彷佛\N置身電影中的感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:04.14,0:25:11.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳輕聲細語地說著\N安靜的最後一幕

